                           <p>A <material>white marble</material>
                              <objectType> altar-stele</objectType> with moulding above and below on three sides (<height unit="metre">0.89</height> x <width unit="metre">0.41</width> x <depth unit="metre">0.385</depth>).; The relief is of a <rs type="decoration">gladiator</rs>, a retiarius, inclined to his left. His right arm is bent and his hand rests on his right hip, with the net hanging over it. In his left hand he holds upright his trident, with two prongs, and a small square object resting on it.</p>
